    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are proud to present this extraordinary specimen, preserved in a state that can only be described as showroom-grade. Every detail, from the lustrous depth of the paintwork to the immaculate condition of the interior upholstery, reflects a history of fastidious care and climate-controlled storage. Mechanically flawless and aesthetically peerless, this vehicle represents a rare opportunity for the serious enthusiast to acquire an example of the marque that remains indistinguishable from new.",
